name: Alice McCall Franks Hall Dress
description:
This gorgeous, strapless and luxurious dress by Alice McCall is super feminine and a fabulous fit.

Fully lined with a boned bodice and sweetheart neckline. Not to mention that the fabric is permanently pleated with elegant knife pleats!

Dry clean only.

Brand new with tags, retails at $389, and is no longer available in stores or online.

In the classic Parisian Print!

name: One Teaspoon Indiana Tube Dress
description:
With a killer assymetrical style and a stretchy, tight fit, this dress is perfect for any night out. Team with some bold accesories and some coloured shoes for a wild look, or with nude or black heels for an anonymous feel.


Retails at $150.

*This product is brand new with tags attached.

name: Seafolly Sorrento Boyleg Maillot
description:
This gorgeous swimsuit is a sold out style, perfect for lying by the beach/pool and practical for swimming in! Amazing fit.

Very flattering, glamorous Seafolly one-piece.
Adjustable halter neck ties for the perfect fit.
Boyleg style leg line for extra coverage. 
In built shelf bra with moulded cups for support, shape & coverage. 
Soft Fabric.
Scallop textured detailing panels.
Elegant Black & White Design.
RRP $149.95.

*This product is brand new with tags and hygiene seal attached.
